name: Town Jjhief
content: Well done.

name: Town Jjhief
content: ……Squeak.

name: Town Jjhief
content: Um, um. You are cool! I can trust you.

name: Town Jjhief
content: Well, squeak, then…….

name: Town Jjhief
content: The Exam monster is very dangerous. You need to hide your identity.

name: Town Jjhief
content: I will give you a new name.

name: Town Jjhief
content: Your new name, squeak, from now on…!

name: Town Jjhief
content: From now on…………………!

name: Town Jjhief
content: [Nickname]!

name: Town Jjhief
content: ……Squeak.

name: Town Jjhief
content: How is it? Do you like it?

name: Town Jjhief
content: [Nickname]. Congratulation on becoming the Mathranger.

name: Town Jjhief
content: Then, i'll explain the mission before you start.

name: Town Jjhief
content: The exam monster is deep in the school. You must go there to combat with it.

name: Town Jjhief
content: The way to go there is very rough. There are many enemies there.

name: Town Jjhief
content: But, you can do! Squeak!

name: Town Jjhief
content: You can <color=#479dda>jump"</color> and <color=#479dda>"slide"</color> well to avoid them."

name: Town Jjhief
content: There is a hearsay that something that looks like a ruler poses horrible <color=#bf4240>questions"</color>. You have to solve the question to pass."

name: Town Jjhief
content: And if you solve it, you can get a <color=#a9ad35>special buff"</color>! Squeak!"

name: Town Jjhief
content: If you have that buff, your battle will be easier...!

name: Town Jjhief
content: Squeak, squeak... And...

name: Town Jjhief
content: Don't forget to collect delicious cheese! It is used for good!

name: Town Jjhief
content: And there are various activities besides defeating the exam monster.

name: Town Jjhief
content: You can decorate yourself with skin items and listen to peaceful music.

name: Town Jjhief
content: It is also possible to check your records and compete against other mathrangers for score.

name: Town Jjhief
content: In addition, you can compete for family scores with the honor of the family!

name: Town Jjhief
content: When you are tired of fighting, try other various activities! Squeak!

name: Town Jjhief
content: Then [Nickname]... It is time to start!

name: Town Jjhief
content: Please repel the Exam monster and bring peace to our town.

name: Town Jjhief
content: ……Squeak.
